g.text: Double spend problem: The wholesaler could provide
the same certificate to different manufacturers.
How do we prevent double spend?
Audit of the wholesaler => show me what you bought and what you sold
Do they add up? (structure + tech solution)
NB: you could also worry about generation of "fake" certificates
but this seems trivially solvable by having the issuing authority
digitally sign their certificates and publish their public key.
NB: "authority" and trust for the initial
HAS to be outside of blockchain.
I want to know what went into my phone and where it came from?
E.g. re there "conflict minerals" in there? How much co2 was involved ...
How is Blockchain/DLT relevant? How is it better or worse
than other solutions (e.g. centralized DB or honest wholesalers)
